# SatyaCheck AI - Environment Variables Template

# ========================================
# CRITICAL VARIABLES (Required for Core Functionality)
# ========================================

# Google AI Studio API Key for Gemini 1.5 Flash
# Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...your_gemini_api_key_here

# Google Cloud Project ID
# Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=your-project-id-here

# ========================================
# IMPORTANT VARIABLES (Enhanced Features)
# ========================================

# Google Custom Search API Key (for PIB fact-check integration)
# Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
GOOGLE_SEARCH_API_KEY=your_search_api_key_here

# Google Custom Search Engine ID (for PIB fact-checking)
# Create at: https://cse.google.com/
GOOGLE_SEARCH_ENGINE_ID=your_search_engine_id_here

# ========================================
# OPTIONAL VARIABLES (Auto-configured in Google Cloud)
# ========================================

# Google Cloud Region (defaults to us-central1)
GOOGLE_CLOUD_REGION=us-central1

# Environment (development/production)
ENVIRONMENT=development

# Google Application Credentials (path to service account JSON)
# Only needed for local development with Google Cloud services
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/service-account-key.json

# ========================================
# API ENDPOINTS (Usually auto-configured)
# ========================================

# Gemini API Endpoint (uses default if not specified)
# GEMINI_API_ENDPOINT=https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-1.5-flash:generateContent

# Google Translate API Endpoint (uses default if not specified)
# GOOGLE_TRANSLATE_ENDPOINT=https://translation.googleapis.com/language/translate/v2

# ========================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ========================================

# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Get Google AI Studio API key from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# 3. Create Google Cloud project at: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 4. Enable required APIs:
#    - AI Platform API
#    - Cloud Vision API
#    - Cloud Speech-to-Text API
#    - Cloud Text-to-Speech API
#    - Cloud Translation API
#    - Custom Search API (optional)
# 5. Fill in your actual values above
# 6. Test with: python validate_deployment.py

# ========================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ========================================

# - NEVER commit .env file to version control
# - Use Google Cloud Secret Manager for production
# - Rotate API keys regularly
# - Use minimal required IAM permissions
# - Monitor API usage and quotas

# ========================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ========================================

# Common issues:
# 1. "GEMINI_API_KEY not found" - Check API key is correctly set
# 2. "API key format invalid" - Ensure key starts with "AIza"
# 3. "Google Cloud services failed" - Check project ID and APIs enabled
# 4. "PIB search disabled" - GOOGLE_SEARCH_API_KEY and ENGINE_ID required
# 5. Run validation script: python validate_deployment.py